snippet.title: 2nd T20 | Hindi | Highlights | India Tour Of Sri Lanka | 28th July 2024
snippet.description:
India and Sri Lanka faced each other in the 2nd T20 at Pallekele International Cricket Stadium. India won the toss and elected to bowl first. Sri Lanka started the batting well but lost their way towards the end. Sri Lanka managed to post 161 runs for the loss of 9 wickets. The match was later affected by rain and hence the target for India was 78 runs in 8 overs. India however showcased a superb batting performance and sealed a 7-wicket victory with 9 balls to spare.
.
.

Jaan Nisar Episode 38 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Danish Taimoor - Hiba Bukhari - Haroon Shahid - 28th July 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Jaan Nisar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

7th Sky Entertainment’s mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznavi’s love?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Mohsin Mirza
Writer: Rehana Aftab

Cast:
Danish Taimoor as Nosherwan Ghaznavi
Hiba Bukhari as Dua
Haroon Shahid as Faraz
Sajid Hasan as Aslam
Hina Bayat as Amma Saeein
Mahmood Aslam as Baba Saeein

snippet.title: Anjali ने बनाया Tapu Sena के लिए Yummy Meal | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Bhide V/s Tapu Sena
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

Anjali buys delicious cooking stuff. Upon finding that Anjali is preparing such mouthwatering food, Mehta becomes enthusiastic and vows to accompany her to the movie. Bhide, however, is not having a good day. In this episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah, find out why Bhide is furious.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 372
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2024 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch more episodes from 'Bhide V/s Tapu Sena' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cSBrJc2CLaW5IzUPoMSw-12

snippet.title: Bairavaa - Super Hit Comedy Scenes | Vijay | Motta Rajendran | Sathish | Thambi Ramaiah | Adithya TV
snippet.description:
A loan recovery officer, Bhairava, finds a girl who wants to expose a local gangster and starts liking her. However, when he listens to her story, Bhairava decides to help her in her endeavours. 

Bairavaa is a 2017 Indian Tamil-language action film written and directed by Bharathan, and produced by B. Venkatarama Reddy. The film stars Vijay in the titular role alongside Keerthy Suresh, Jagapathi Babu, Daniel Balaji, Sathish, Thambi Ramaiah, Mime Gopi, Sija Rose, Harish Uthaman and Aparna Vinod.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: North Indian Vs South Indian Food Eating Challenge 🔥|| FoodieWe 24hrs Challenge
snippet.description:
North Indian Vs South Indian Food Eating Challenge || Foodiewe 24hrs Challenge
1000 Rupees Challenge 

Welcome to another exciting food challenge on FoodieWe! 🎉 This time, we're diving deep into the vibrant flavors of South Indian and North Indian cuisines. Mukti has set a thrilling challenge for Onkar and Aditya: survive on just ₹1000 for an entire day! But there's a twist—Aditya must savor only South Indian delicacies, while Onkar enjoys the rich tastes of North Indian fare.


From crispy dosas and spicy sambars to buttery naans and flavorful curries, this video is packed with mouthwatering and tempting dishes that will leave you craving more. Watch as Onkar and Aditya navigate their budgets, explore the diverse culinary landscapes, and compete to see who can eat the most delicious food.

Warning: Do not watch this video if you're hungry—resisting these tantalizing treats will be nearly impossible! 🍛🍲

Join us on this culinary adventure and find out who will emerge victorious in the ultimate food challenge. Don't forget to like, comment, and subscribe to FoodieWe for more epic food battles and delicious content!

#FoodChallenge #FoodieWe

Location 

1) Preet ( Time Till 2pm )- phase 7 mohali
2) Sardaji Dahi Bhalli (Time 11 am)- 3b1 Mohali
3) Shardai - 3b2 Mohali ( opp market near park )
4) nagpal - sector 34 chandigarh 
5) brother kulcha - sector 9 chandigarh 
6) gol gappe & jalebi - sector 32 street vendors market

snippet.title: Gully Bonalu || Neeraj Bandari || Chandu Charms || Telugu Short Films 2024 || Infinitum Media
snippet.description:
"Gully Bonalu" takes you on an immersive journey through the local streets and alleys (gullies) of Telangana during the vibrant Bonalu festival. This film captures the spirit and fervor of the celebrations as experienced by the local communities, showcasing their unwavering devotion and cultural richness.

Watch:- Gully Bonalu || Neeraj Bandari || Chandu Charms || Telugu Short Films 2024 || Infinitum Media 

Cast: Neeraj Bandari, Chandu Charms, Uma Mahesh, Actor Bhargav, Chandra Bhanu, Naveen Darga, Yashwanth.

Produced by Vandana Bandaru

Written & Directed by Neeraj Bandari

DOP:- Ronaddhirr 

Editor:- Madhu Kallepalli, Raj Krish.

Publicity Designer:- Shiva Krishna 

Sound Engineer:- Venkat 

Assistant DOP: Yashwanth Ravella.

Line Producer:- Naveen Darga

Executive Producer: Sathwik G Roy, Abhilash Rao Desineni.

#GullyBonalu #NeerajBandari #ChanduCharms #TeluguShortFilms #LatestTeluguShortFilms2024 #InfinitumMedia #Bonalu #Bonalu2024 #BonaluCelebrations #HyderabadBonalu #TelanganaBonalu2024 #BonaluFestival #BonaluVideos

Presented by Infinitum Network Solutions.

snippet.title: राजपाल यादव की बंदरगिरी: जब जेल में हुई Rajpal Yadav की जमकर धुलाई😜लोटपोट कॉमेडी | Chor Machaye Shor
snippet.description:
Watch the hilarious comedy scene featuring Rajpal Yadav, Paresh Rawal and Bobby Deol from the movie "Chor Machaaye Shor". This rib-tickling film is directed by David Dhawan, with music composed by Anu Malik, and produced by Sujit Kumar.

देखिए राजपाल यादव, परेश रावल और बॉबी देओल का मजेदार कॉमेडी सीन फिल्म "चोर मचाए शोर" से। इस हंसी-मजाक से भरी फिल्म का निर्देशन डेविड धवन ने किया है, संगीत अनु मलिक द्वारा रचित है, और इसका निर्माण सुजीत कुमार ने किया है।

Movie: Chor Machaaye Shor (2002)

Cast: Paresh Rawal, Bobby Deol, Shilpa Shetty, Bipasha Basu, Om Puri, Rajpal Yadav, Shekhar Suman, Razak Khan

Music: Anu Malik

Director: David Dhawan

Producer: Sanjiv Tolani, Rajiv Tolani

*About* 
------------

       Police officer Virat Chavan ne diya vaada apne marte hue junior ko ke rakhenge woh khayal unki beti, Sai ka. Virat aur Sai bandh gaye anchaahe shaadi ke bandhan mai. Virat ka dil tha Patralekha ke paas jiski shaadi hojati hai kisi aur se. Virat ne vaada kiya Pakhi se ke woh uski jagah kabhi kisi aur ko nahi dega. 
                Virat ne bhale nahi diya Sai ko ek pati ka pyaar par unke rishtey mai izzat hamesha thi. Waqt ke saath saath, Virat ne dekha Sai ka accha roop aur hogaya ussey Sai se pyaar. Yeh kahani hai Virat, Sai aur Patralekha ke pyaar ki.

                Virat ne bhale nahi diya Sai ko ek pati ka pyaar par unke rishtey mai izzat hamesha thi. Waqt ke saath saath, Virat ne dekha Sai ka accha roop aur hogaya ussey Sai se pyaar. Yeh kahani hai Virat, Sai aur Patralekha ke pyaar ki.

snippet.description:

Episode 4147: Goli And Sakharam Return
--------------------------------------------------------
The colony members express concern about Goli and Sakharam's whereabouts to Inspector Pandey. Fortunately, Goli returns shortly, easing everyone's worries. How will Inspector Pandey react when he finds out Goli has returned?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4147 | 26 July 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

snippet.title: Billa Sonipat Ala : Shiva The Damru Ala (Official Video) Deepty | Haryanvi Songs | Bholenath Songs
snippet.description:
🌟 Feel the divine energy! White Hill Dhaakad presents new Haryanvi song "Shiva the Damru Ala" by Billa Sonipat Ala. Let the power of Bholenath uplift your spirit! 🚀🎶 


#ShivaTheDamruAla #BillaSonipatAla #WhiteHillDhaakad #BholenathSongs #Divine #KaavadSongs

Click here to create reels : https://tinyurl.com/yut7vb6p

Credits :

Singer/Lyrics/Composer : Billa Sonipat Ala

Mix & Master : D Chandu

Creative Director : Director Lakshay 
Dop : Nishan Singh
Production: Rohit Mantro (Team All Good)

Design : Unacnny Rahul, Rohit Chouhan

🎵 Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/track/5vZAbvsEkHgft02LU8m69X?si=b2770139b2514acb
🍏 Apple Music: https://music.apple.com/in/album/shiva-the-damru-ala/1756900725
🎼 iTunes: https://music.apple.com/in/album/shiva-the-damru-ala/1756900725?i=1756900879
🔊 Amazon Prime Music: https://music.amazon.in/tracks/B0D9BRNK9H?marketplaceId=A21TJRUUN4KGV&musicTerritory=IN&ref=dm_sh_2nTbtWtuks5gr8A0PUUx8njSW
🎧 YouTube Music: https://music.youtube.com/watch?v=tyBWvZawgWk&si=piM8q64e_V7Q66aB
🎶 JioSaavn: https://www.jiosaavn.com/song/shiva-the-damru-ala/Eg4gQjFyUgU
🎧 Gaana: https://gaana.com/song/shiva-the-damru-ala
🎵 Wynk: https://wynk.in/u/6Jncxboz7


👁️‍🗨️ Lyrics :
Main aaya hu tere duwar pe bhole
Mere dil mein hai tasveer teri
2 pal ka lake samay shiva
Tu badal de ne taqdeer meri 
Duniya ne main chhod ke aaya mera hai sansar tu
Bhole mera hath pakad ke lade manne paar tu
Na koye meri sunan ala yade banja mera yaar tu

Haar jade meri pakki thi main ude jeet ke aaya hu
Matlab ki duniya te bhole manne khinch ke laya tu
Tu aave mere sapnya mein manne or na koy suhata re
Miljavega kise mod pe tanne dhundhe jau rata ne
Ek tarfa karde game shiva meri banwa de sarkar tu 
Bhole mera hath pakad ke lade manne paar tu
Na koye meri sunan ala yade banja mera yaar tu

Tera ant na tu hai anant shiva
Main ke tha ke tanne kardiya 
Main ro padya tanne dekh shiva
Mera ghar khushiyan te bhardiya 
Har kaam se baba shuru karya 
Tera naam hai pehle pe rakhya 
He re jabbe billa sonipat ale ne dhumma tha rakhya 
Tere naam te roti chale hai na itna bada fankar su
Bhole mera hath pakad ke lade manne paar tu
Na koye meri sunan ala yade banja mera yaar tu
Bhole mera hath pakad ke lade manne paar tu
Na koye meri sunan ala yade banja mera yaar tu
Ho damru ala mera yaar bhole baba ki sarkar
Damru ala mera yaar bhole baba ki sarkar

snippet.title: NEW & EXCLUSIVE! *Introducing GOLI* I Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - EP 4147 | तारक मेहता
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Watch the full episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSKo8X_EiY0WewaBlNt49g3

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Navina Wadekar / Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

snippet.title: TOP ENGLISH 50 VOCAB | VOCABULARY WORDS ENGLISH | LEARN WITH MEANING | MUST KNOW VOCAB FOR STUDENTS
snippet.description:
Welcome to Dear Sir! 🚀 In this comprehensive video, we're presenting the "TOP ENGLISH 50 VOCAB" - a curated list of essential vocabulary words every student should know. 🌟 Whether you're preparing for competitive exams like IELTS, TOEFL, or just aiming to enhance your English language skills, this video is packed with the most useful and impactful words to enrich your vocabulary.

Each word is explained with its meaning, pronunciation, and real-life usage examples, making it easier for you to understand and remember. This video is perfect for students, professionals, and anyone keen on mastering the English language. By the end of this session, you'll have a strong grasp of 50 must-know English words that can significantly improve your writing and speaking skills.

Why you should watch this video:

- Boost Your Vocabulary: Learn 50 high-frequency words used in daily conversation and academic writing.
- Improve Pronunciation: Hear the correct pronunciation of each word, helping you sound more confident and fluent.
- Understand Usage: See how these words are used in sentences to better grasp their meanings and applications.
- Exam Preparation: Perfect for students preparing for IELTS, TOEFL, and other competitive exams, providing a solid vocabulary foundation.

Make sure to watch till the end and take notes! 📚

🔔 Don't forget to subscribe to Dear Sir and hit the bell icon 🔔 for more educational videos and study tips! If you found this video helpful, please give it a thumbs up 👍, share it with your friends, and leave a comment with your favorite word from the list or any questions you might have.

snippet.title: Goli's Farewell Celebration - Kush Shah | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Watch the full episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSKo8X_EiY0WewaBlNt49g3

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Navina Wadekar / Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

Produced By: Neela Asit Modi, Asit Kumarr Modi 
Special Thanks: Mahesh Vakil, Indu Tarak Mehta
Set Design: Jayant Deshmukh

Costume Designer: Alka Mehta

snippet.title: Joker: Folie À Deux | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
When you’re smiling, the whole world smiles with you. Joker: Folie À Deux – only in theaters and IMAX, October 4. #JokerMovie #FilmedForIMAX 

From acclaimed writer/director/producer Todd Phillips comes “Joker: Folie À Deux,” the much-anticipated follow-up to 2019’s Academy Award-winning “Joker,” which earned more than $1 billion at the global box office and remains the highest-grossing R-rated film of all time.  The new film stars Joaquin Phoenix once again in his Oscar-winning dual role as Arthur Fleck/Joker, opposite Oscar winner Lady Gaga (“A Star Is Born”).

“Joker: Folie À Deux” finds Arthur Fleck institutionalized at Arkham awaiting trial for his crimes as Joker. While struggling with his dual identity, Arthur not only stumbles upon true love, but also finds the music that's always been inside him.

The film also stars Oscar nominees Brendan Gleeson (“The Banshees of Inisherin”) and Catherine Keener (“Get Out,” “Capote”), alongside Zazie Beetz, reprising her role from “Joker.”

Phillips, who was nominated for Oscars for directing, writing and producing “Joker,” directed “Joker: Folie À Deux” from a screenplay by fellow Oscar nominee Scott Silver & Phillips, based on characters from DC.  The film was produced by Phillips, Oscar nominee Emma Tillinger Koskoff and Joseph Garner.  Lady Gaga served as music consultant.  The film’s executive producers are Michael E. Uslan, Georgia Kacandes, Silver, Mark Friedberg and Jason Ruder.

Working with Phillips behind the camera are his team from “Joker,” including Oscar-nominated director of photography Lawrence Sher, production designer Mark Friedberg, Oscar-nominated editor Jeff Groth, and composer Hildur Guđnadóttir, who won the Oscar for her work on the first film.  New to the team is Oscar-nominated costume designer Arianne Phillips (“Once Upon a Time in… Hollywood,” “Don’t Worry Darling”).  Ruder is the film’s executive music producer and the music supervisors are Randall Poster and George Drakoulias.  Casting is by Francine Maisler (the “Dune” films, “Challengers”).

Warner Bros. Pictures Presents A Joint Effort Production, A Film by Todd Phillips, “Joker: Folie À Deux.”  The film will be released worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures, and will be only in theaters nationwide on October 4, 2024, and beginning internationally on 2 October, 2024.

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4146: Goli Kaha Hai?
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide searches for Sakharam and discovers that Goli has gone to get breakfast on Sakharam. Later, they find Sakharam crashed with no sign of Goli. Will they be able to locate Goli?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4146 | 25 July 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
